# whisk — environment configuration
#
# The OpenAI layer is OPTIONAL. Leave these blank and whisk runs fully on
# deterministic Wikipedia-only signals (search, clustering, rabbit-hole
# narration all still work). Add a key to enable AI query expansion, smarter
# cluster labels, "why this matched" explanations, and richer path narration.
#
# ⚠️  SECURITY: VITE_* variables are embedded in the client bundle, so this key
# is visible to anyone who loads the app. This is fine for LOCAL / personal use.
# Before any PUBLIC deploy, move OpenAI calls behind a small serverless proxy
# and drop the key from the client. See README.md.

VITE_OPENAI_API_KEY=
VITE_OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini
